		 * Calculate Annual Direct Taxes based on the  Tax Installments, Annual tax liability deducted based on the installment percentage.
		 * @param cube, scenario, version, entity will be passed from form context.
		 * @param  startperiod and end periods, Daily, weekly and Monthly first and last period of corresponding period dimension.
		 * @param fixParallelDim  - name of the dimension on which fix parallel to be applied.
		 * @return  - returns calculation script to compute Direct Tax payments, populate results into rolling forecast screen based on forecast method settings, and calculation logic to compute opening balance.
		 * Additional Notes
		 *		1. Groovy script generates calc script based on the request type, if request comes onsave rule, script generated on specific intersection, if request is coming from rules, card script runs 
		 *		for all intersections, if request is coming from DM, request gets executed for specific date.
		 *	 	2. Based on fix parallel dimension, logic gets aligned accordingly.
		 *		3. Tax installments are computed based on installement date. In case of Periodic model, installment will be posted in corresponding week or month.
		 *		4. While calculating 2nd Installment, previous installment amount will be subtracted to arrive next installement amount.
		 *		5. Computed tax amount will be copied to forecast based on the configuration.
		 *		6. Recalculate Opening balance  
		 **/
		String calculateDirectTaxes(Cube cashFlowCube,String scenarioMember,String versionMember,String entityMember,String startPeriod,String endPeriod,String fixParallelDim,String flexDim1Member,String flexDim2Member,String flexDim3Member,String partyMember,String buMember,String prjMember,String currencyMember)
		{
				String calcCopyString,calcOpenBal,fixParalleFixStmt,catStartFix,catEndFix  ;
				boolean chkEntityIsFixParallel=false,chkCategoryFixParallel=false;
